    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this incredible find! This vehicle is in truly mint condition, looking and driving as if it just left the showroom for the first time. Every detail has been meticulously preserved, from the flawless exterior to the pristine interior, making it a rare opportunity for a buyer who demands the very best.",
